# Javascript Example

There are a script with 2 versions:

```javascript fence_title="ES5"
// A code from ES5
var demo="cool"
```
```javascript fence_title="ES6"
/*
    A single example with 'let'
    keyword on ES6
*/
let demo="cool"
```
